  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Brew #126: Meet the DAO Council Candidates – TLDR\nBeth posted a video recapping the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas: Crew Pack Opening: Let’s GO!\nOCG Thor posted a video on opening his crew packs.\nStar Atlas: Bitch and Moan About Crew Airdrop\nOCG Thor posted a video about his thoughts on the crew airdrop.\nStar Atlas Tensor Tutorial (part 2)\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of his second part Tensor tutorial.\nMetaverse Nomads #162 Star Atlas\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nWeekly Star Atlas Newsletter #145\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nThe Atlas Brew #127\nStar Atlas TV posted a video of the latest Atlas Brew.\n3D Printed Star Atlas TREEARROW\nEnigma 42 posted a video about a 3D printed Treearrow he made.\nStar Atlas Economic Forum (September 2024)\nStar Atlas TV posted a video of the latest Star Atlas Economic Forum.",
